title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 4 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3: Ann Coulter joins C&B, talks Cuomo, mask mandates, vaccine passports, Democrat hypocrisy. CNN commentator says unvaccinated should be on no-fly list. Coulter on immigration, repatriation, the future of the GOP and American Olympic wrestler Tamyra Mensah-Stock, who told the world how much she loved America after her gold-medal win.
